item.description:
创建数据库 create database &ldquo;dbname&rdquo;;
创建用户 create user &ldquo;username&rdquo;@&ldquo;host&rdquo; identified by &ldquo;password&rdquo;;
赋予用户权限 grant all privileges on dbname.* to &ldquo;dbuser&rdquo;@&ldquo;host&rdquo; with grant option;
查看权限 show grants for &ldquo;username&rdquo;@&ldquo;host&rdquo;;
删除权限 revoke all on dbname.table from &lsquo;user&rsquo;@'%';
备份还原 -d 备份表结构 -t 备份数据
备份数据库 mysqldump -hys1.51asj.com -P3306 -uroot -p &ndash;databases dbname &gt; /tmp/dbname.sql
备份数据库单表 mysqldump -hys1.51asj.com -P3306 -uroot -p dbname tablename &gt; /tmp/tablename.sql
还原数据 mysql&gt; source /tmp/dbname.sql
